      <title>170 万美元豪宅引发竞价热潮 韩国拍卖网站瘫痪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bidding-frenzy-for-1-7-million-homes-crashes-korea-auction-site</link>
